 NewsSocial – Social News Website

NewsSocial is a news website built with C# and .NET Core that simulates a social media experience.
Users can read news articles, like, comment, share posts, add friends, and even get AI-generated summaries of articles.

Features

Display news articles with images and content

Like, comment, and share posts

Add and manage friends

User authentication & simple profiles

AI-powered article summaries

Responsive design for desktop & mobile

 Tech Stack

Backend: C#, .NET Core

Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript

Database: SQL Server (or specify your DB)

 Live Demo

Check the website here: https://proj.ruppin.ac.il/cgroup23/test2/tar5/index.html
